Package verify

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TraceFormatter
    Defines methods to parse the output generated by the model checker into outcome(s), flip(s), cycle(s), etc.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CadenceSMVTraceFormatter
    A parser for traces generated by Cadence SMV model checker.
    ModelChecker
    ModelChecker is the interface between the preference reasoner in Java and the model checker tool that runs on the OS shell.
    ModelCheckingDelegate
    Verifies SMV model using the given constraints against the given specifications, and parses the verification result
    NuSMVTraceFormatter
    A parser for traces generated by NuSMV model checker.
    SpecHelper
    Generates SMV model code for initializing a model to the set of states corresponding to an outcome.
    TraceFormatterFactory
    Factory class that provides CadenceSMVTraceFormatter or NuSMVTraceFormatter (for now) implementations
